{
  "$type": "program",
  "children": [
    {
      "comment": "# Two invariants:"
    },
    {
      "comment": "#"
    },
    {
      "comment": "# 1. Every Ruby `identifier` becomes <name> unconditionally (no"
    },
    {
      "comment": "#    type_identifier in Ruby's grammar, so identifiers are always"
    },
    {
      "comment": "#    value references). Matches Python / TS / Java / Rust on the"
    },
    {
      "comment": "#    value-namespace side (Principle #14)."
    },
    {
      "comment": "#"
    },
    {
      "comment": "# 2. When a <name> wrapper sits inside method / class / module and"
    },
    {
      "comment": "#    contains a single identifier, the transform inlines its text"
    },
    {
      "comment": "#    directly: <method><name>foo</name>… not"
    },
    {
      "comment": "#    <method><name><identifier>foo</identifier></name>…"
    },
    {
      "$type": "class",
      "name": "Calculator",
      "body": {
        "children": [
          {
            "$type": "method",
            "name": "add",
            "parameters": [
              "a",
              "b"
            ],
            "body": {
              "children": [
                {
                  "$type": "binary",
                  "left": {
                    "name": "a"
                  },
                  "right": {
                    "name": "b"
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "$type": "module",
      "name": "Utils",
      "body": {
        "children": [
          {
            "$type": "singleton_method",
            "object": "self",
            "name": {
              "name": "greet"
            },
            "parameters": "name",
            "body": {
              "children": [
                {
                  "$type": "string",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "string_content": "hi,"
                    },
                    {
                      "$type": "interpolation",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "name": "name"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}